Name: django-sendgrid-v4
Version: 0.5.0a
Summary: An implementation of Django's EmailBackend compatible with sendgrid-python v4+
Home-page: https://github.com/sklarsa/django-sendgrid-v4
Author: Steven Sklar
Author-email: sklarsa@gmail.com
License: WTFPL
Description: .. |travis| image:: https://travis-ci.org/sklarsa/django-sendgrid-v4.svg?branch=master
        
        How to Install
        --------------
        
        1. `pip install django-sendgrid-v4`
        2. In your project's `settings.py` script:
        
         	a. Set `EMAIL_BACKEND = "sendgrid_backend.SendgridBackend"`
         	b. Add `SENDGRID_API_KEY = os.environ["SENDGRID_API_KEY"]`
        
